{"tid":957243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（痴撚線系列）連燈仔竟然讚八萬五","createTime":"2018-12-27T01:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T13:05:39.000Z","uid":51200,"like":41,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"82959c32094f66a9416aed8dcc786d79abc8e638","tid":957243,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T01:15:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母八萬五知唔知幾時推出？<br />\n推出嘅時候撞正亞洲金融風暴，再加Sars <br />\n香港經濟基本上已經冧左<br />\n全香港人連政府一齊收緊皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你再推冧個樓市，<br />\n令到中產進一步資產貶值<br />\n基本上會加長個衰退期好多<br />\n2003年打後點解會幾年就recover 到？唔係十年二十年？<br />\n知唔知咩叫緊縮性同擴張性政策？<br />\n<br />\n無可否認八萬五係而家呢啲時期係應該推出，壓抑樓市（正路係應該曾蔭權時代已經要推出）<br />\n但一個好嘅政策一定要睇佢個時間<br />\n八萬五嘅錯誤推出時間絕對會令到香港萬劫不復<br />\n<br />\n要怪點解無公屋住<br />\n主要係因為曾蔭權停建左公屋一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去谷樓市，加快復甦<br />\n第一步做錯左，之後班仆街跟著做<br />\n連公屋供應量都減少埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n八萬五當年真係推出左，全香港人<br />\n你同我係絕對死硬<br />\n要推，應該都係曾蔭權推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869fdbd46b3e527f7ff9b606552f56e7f8124f68","tid":957243,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T01:17:34.000Z","msg":"2017 to 2023 = 1997 to 2003<br />\n100% match !<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc0ca3a2497de75d7dcd4b1007a604c30fdb26d","tid":957243,"uid":68556,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T01:18:32.000Z","msg":"其實即使當年經濟無變差， 八萬五都唔會持續達成到建屋目標。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd852e4d590c7b1a7e477f12f72337515b97523","tid":957243,